who have taken my father to this place,

17:29.548 --> 17:30.966
and they're gonna kill him.

17:31.967 --> 17:34.219
So I need your help
to find this place, Neville.

17:34.219 --> 17:35.429
No, no, no, no.

17:36.597 --> 17:37.514
No?

17:39.725 --> 17:41.727
The curse has already done enough.

17:42.227 --> 17:44.313
No, no, no. Look, it's not a curse. Okay?

17:44.313 --> 17:46.648
